data.description: This farmhouse gem is perfectly situated on a corner lot with ample parking space. The oversized two-car garage comes complete with a workshop area. The sunroom offers a tranquil escape, showcasing views of the backyard. This home boasts both a family room and a living room. The living room's high ceilings and glass doors provide a connection to the sunroom, flooding the space with natural light. The kitchen is adorned with stainless steel appliances and charming butcher block countertops. The master bedroom is a haven of comfort, generously accommodating a king-sized bed and a private sitting area. Double doors lead to the covered porch, offering a seamless indoor-outdoor flow. Elegance, and a touch of rustic charm, making it a remarkable canvas to create your dream home!
